.TH SCRIBED "1" "January 2018" "scribed 0.12"
.SH NAME
scribed \- peer-to-peer network based digital currency
.SH SYNOPSIS
scribed [options] <command> [params]
.TP
scribed [options] help <command> \- Get help for a command
.SH DESCRIPTION
This  manual page documents the scribed program. Scribe is an experimental new digital currency that enables anonymous, instant payments to anyone, anywhere in the world. Scribe uses peer-to-peer technology to operate with no central authority: managing transactions and issuing money are carried out collectively by the network. Scribe Core is the name of the open source software which enables the use of this currency.

